{"tid":2104501,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鴻海傳投資 10 億美元，印度設 iPhone 組裝廠","createTime":"2020-07-12T04:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T08:22:39.000Z","uid":141151,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6c0889758a9adf98ed76e9c208e5fd14970452ce","tid":2104501,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:24:21.000Z","msg":"鴻海傳投資 10 億美元，印度設 iPhone 組裝廠<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2020/07/11/%e9%b4%bb%e6%b5%b7%e5%82%b3%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87-10-%e5%84%84%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%ef%bc%8c%e5%8d%b0%e5%ba%a6%e8%a8%ad-iphone-%e7%b5%84%e8%a3%9d%e5%bb%a0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2020%2F07%2F11%2F%25e9%25b4%25bb%25e6%25b5%25b7%25e5%2582%25b3%25e6%258a%2595%25e8%25b3%2587-10-%25e5%2584%2584%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%2585%2583%25ef%25bc%258c%25e5%258d%25b0%25e5%25ba%25a6%25e8%25a8%25ad-iphone-%25e7%25b5%2584%25e8%25a3%259d%25e5%25bb%25a0%2F&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnvtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=9f43474f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2020/07/11/%e9%b4%bb%e6%b5%b7%e5%82%b3%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87-10-%e5%84%84%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%ef%bc%8c%e5%8d%b0%e5%ba%a6%e8%a8%ad-iphone-%e7%b5%84%e8%a3%9d%e5%bb%a0/</a><br />\n<br />\n據路透社報導，鴻海計劃在印度南部成立蘋果手機組裝廠，估計耗資 10 億美元。對此，鴻海回應，不評論關於客戶、產品、供應鏈夥伴的市場媒體傳言。<br />\n<br />\n根據路透社報導，受中美貿易戰以及疫情影響，手機代工廠被迫尋找中國以外的生產基地。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述知情人士說法，鴻海規劃將在印度斯利柏倫菩德（Sriperumbudur）成立蘋果手機組裝廠，預估 3 年內完成，屆時將增加 6,000 個工作機會，投資額總計 10 億美元。<br />\n<br />\n針對路透社報導，鴻海回應，一向不評論任何有關既有及潛在客戶、產品、供應鏈夥伴的市場媒體傳言。<br />\n<br />\n鴻海董事長劉揚偉日前在股東會上表示，東南亞設廠關鍵在政府效能，集團在觀察印度當地疫情影響，印度發展可期，未來幾個月在印度投資將會有進展，屆時會跟外界報告。<br />\n<br />\n針對鴻海全球布局方面，他指出，集團在印度和歐洲等地設廠，在東南亞越南據點最大，其次是印度。鴻海北美於墨西哥據點最大，其次是美國。"},{"pid":"a7d1c0385ea355fa621c11d8284d63de223755f0","tid":2104501,"uid":33325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:54:12.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"2b514cd661e53484a607631b36193cb9c6239c08","tid":2104501,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T05:10:32.000Z","msg":"問准咗維尼未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf6bb3c8d1a3b878c81c502b18657858c5d1b4b","tid":2104501,"uid":88737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T05:12:08.000Z","msg":"鴻海富士康一早可以玩無人工廠，只係支那人仲賤頂爛市先唔走<br />\n<br />\n而家中共搵d台資開刀回血，鴻海等左呢d走佬機會好耐"},{"pid":"a4553d7e01952f49872a480bb71dd39d84cad1d6","tid":2104501,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T05:14:57.000Z","msg":"印度啲基建同廿年前冇分別<br />\n冇update過咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aac223804fde686c40436ccf15026c0f4c5db88","tid":2104501,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T08:06:10.000Z","msg":"move out from China <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"563a6cf08c5a0e007e01ad38832b61a864e5e944","tid":2104501,"uid":311223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T08:13:39.000Z","msg":"印度唔係反緊支那？<br />\n比你投資咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d8b6aacf925d1efe6b480788440a6f049c40f8","tid":2104501,"uid":30104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"563a6cf08c5a0e007e01ad38832b61a864e5e944","tid":2104501,"uid":311223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T08:13:39.000Z","msg":"印度唔係反緊支那？<br />\n比你投資咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><